{"tid":415135,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"眼前有似曾相識嘅情景","createTime":"2017-09-26T17:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T17:45:42.000Z","uid":149803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"846db049c7af73db0941839f2b445cb4a404e9cf","tid":415135,"uid":149803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:39:06.000Z","msg":"有冇人成日覺得眼前嘅事物、環境、當下發生嘅事情都似曾相識？"},{"pid":"669d2a27e9b1979ca849919a64a74685cdc6ecd4","tid":415135,"uid":148042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:39:38.000Z","msg":"既視感"},{"pid":"33e1eb93e12cd9b8e2cedf1227224937e70b2bdd","tid":415135,"uid":149803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>既視感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成日都有依種feel"},{"pid":"8a11019ba03a1dd17b8a03f7520de79115d02414","tid":415135,"uid":85416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:40:49.000Z","msg":"夢見過"},{"pid":"a0cb1e87870e6e4087c9cffd96ade42375270028","tid":415135,"uid":148042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:41:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>既視感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成日都有依種feel</blockquote><br />\n有人把這種現象當作靈魂漫遊或前世記憶的證明。腦科學界普遍認為這是因為記憶的存儲出現了短暫的混亂，導致大腦把剛剛得到的信息當成了久遠的回憶。所以這種情況多半是在人們感到疲倦、壓力，或是被不熟悉事物環繞的情況下出現，因為此時大腦無法一一處理接收來的資訊量。相較於老年人，年輕族群比較容易出現「既視感」；一來是年輕人的行程比較飄忽不定，周遭常出現陌生的東西，二來則是年輕人的生活較為忙碌，大腦常常會「打結」<br />\nFROM WIKI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949377ad1d9199a06441840721380da3ff840efb","tid":415135,"uid":149803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:41:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夢見過</blockquote><br />\n有時啲夢會間唔時重複。但又幾正"},{"pid":"b89052cb8d24a3744bcaf08cde66514983c462f0","tid":415135,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:42:33.000Z","msg":"試過好多次 但係都係細個發嘅夢 而家先發生"},{"pid":"e01c2f54026821b81208256c7865d78b46e4f1a9","tid":415135,"uid":16092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco